                            <span class="term">Speed:</span>
                            <span class="value has-tip" data-tooltip aria-haspopup="true" data-disable-hover="false" tabindex="1" title="Speeds approximately 10-13 mph (or in a group ride, the pace of the slowest rider)">Slow</span>
